{
  "description": "A close-up shot of a heavily textured, reddish-pink gourd rests amongst dry, golden straw. The gourd is irregularly shaped, covered in a dense pattern of raised, bumpy protrusions that resemble scales or warts. These protrusions are a lighter, desaturated tan color, contrasting with the warmer reddish-pink base of the gourd. A small, dried stem protrudes from the top. The straw surrounding the gourd is scattered and creates a textured background of warm golden hues. The lighting is soft, highlighting the gourd's unique surface and the straw\u2019s dryness.",
